3
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 1]

4
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:37,800
With long eyebrows

5
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,920
and beautiful, striking eyes,

6
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,560
the man was charming

7
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:47,360
and irresistible.

8
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,240
Zhousheng Chen,

9
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,320
the Junior Prince of Nanchen,

10
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,160
fought bravely for his country.

11
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,320
Loyal as he was,

12
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,520
he became obsessed with fame

13
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,920
and wealth in his prime,

14
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,240
thus the seed of rebellion began to grow in him.

15
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:21,079
Fortunately, the prestigious family in Qinghe saw through his plot.

16
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,800
As a result, the Junior Prince of Nanchen got arrested.

17
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,200
The crown prince was furious with him,

18
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,760
and sentenced him to death by dismemberment.

19
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,400
The execution lasted for six hours,

20
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:43,120
but the Junior Prince of Nanchen never let out a cry of pain once.

21
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,520
He regretted nothing even till his last breath.

22
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,200
You need to hurry,

23
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,600
or you'll miss the flight.

24
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,440
Was it okay?

25
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,360
Your work

26
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,360
has always been perfect!

27
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,240
Then I'm leaving.

28
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,280
I'll finish the rest in Shanghai.

29
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,400
Okay! Have a nice trip!

30
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,079
I've asked them to take your luggage down

31
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:18,880
to save some time.

32
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,280
Thank you! Bye-bye!

33
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,280
-Bye-bye!
-Bye-bye!

34
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,000
No one can top

35
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,360
Miss Shi's voice.

36
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,079
Of course!

37
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,760
The producer pleaded with her four times.

38
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,480
His persistence finally got her here.

39
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:36,579
[Guangzhou]

40
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,800
He's a loyal official

41
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:59,560
who protected his country and had no wife or children.

42
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:00,960
But in the end

43
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,560
he was framed.

44
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,839
Zhousheng Chen...

45
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,320
The Junior Prince of Nanchen.

46
00:04:15,540 --> 00:04:22,100
[Liede Bridge]

47
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:27,540
[Check-in Desk]

48
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,840
Hi. I'm here for the 3 pm flight to Shanghai.

49
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:25,640
Hi.

50
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,159
Please put your luggage on the conveyor belt.

51
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:32,940
[Out of service]

52
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,159
Hi.

53
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,240
I'm here for the 3 pm flight to Xi'an.

54
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,080
-Hi. -Thanks!
-Sure!

55
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:52,940
[Out of service]

56
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,400
Here's your boarding pass.

57
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,040
Thank you!

58
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,560
Mr. Zhousheng!

59
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,440
Sorry! I'm late!

60
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,800
Give me your ID card.

61
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,600
Hi. We're on same flight.

62
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,280
To Xi'an.

63
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:01,840
Okay.

64
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,760
Sir, your ID card.

65
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,360
Here you go.

66
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:20,120
Let me help you with that.

67
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,240
Please go through the metal detector again.

68
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,280
Did you take your cellphone out?

69
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,040
I did.

70
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,080
I don't have anything on me.

71
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,480
Please take off your high heels.

72
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,159
Okay.

73
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,200
Turn around, please.

74
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,880
Turn around, please.

75
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,160
Please go through it again.

76
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,000
Turn around, please.

77
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,560
Thank you!

78
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:33,920
Mr. Zhousheng Chen!

79
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,240
You forgot your ID card!

80
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,120
Thank you!

81
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,680
Mr. Zhousheng,

82
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,960
I'm so sorry.

83
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,000
I was going

84
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,160
to carry your stuff for you,

85
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:19,920
but I almost left

86
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,440
your ID card there.

87
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,400
Sir! Sir!

88
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,520
Wait a moment!

89
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,920
May I borrow a few seconds of your time?

90
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,960
It may sound a little abrupt,

91
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,680
but is your name Zhousheng Chen?

92
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,200
I heard they call you that

93
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,440
at the security check.

94
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:38,960
Yes.

95
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,400
I'm Zhousheng Chen.

96
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,320
Here's the thing.

97
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,560
I've seen your name

98
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,159
a lot recently during work.

99
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,480
Zhousheng Chen.

100
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:48,159
It's a character's name in a story.

101
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,200
A movie, to be exact.

102
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,840
I've been dubbing for the movie.

103
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,960
So I just had to talk to you

104
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,480
when I heard the name Zhousheng Chen.

105
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,400
Sorry! I've made it even more confusing.

106
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,400
You may not know this,

107
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:01,560
but I...

108
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,800
The story about the Junior Prince of Nanchen?

109
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,840
Yes! You know that story?

110
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:07,840
I do.

111
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,160
Nice to meet you! My name is Shi Yi.

112
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,440
Nice to meet you!

113
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,840
I'll be boarding soon,

114
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:18,960
and I don't have much time.

115
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,560
May I have your WeChat contact

116
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:22,840
or phone number?

117
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,480
I hope we can be friends.

118
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,240
Just friends!

119
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,159
I'm sorry.

120
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,520
I've just come back from abroad

121
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,360
and I don't have

122
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,040
a local number yet.

123
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,320
I see.

124
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,520
That's all right.

125
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,680
If you don't mind

126
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,400
contacting via email,

127
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:46,560
we can exchange

128
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,640
our E-mail addresses.

129
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:50,600
Sure!

130
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,160
I give you mine, or you give me yours?

131
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,880
I'll give you mine.

132
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,880
Pen and paper, please.

133
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,280
Final call for flight CA 1866.

134
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,520
Would Miss Shi Yi

135
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,360
please go to the boarding gate as soon as possible.

136
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,600
The flight will take off soon.

137
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:13,560
Here.

138
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,440
Thank you!

139
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,800
I'll be going then.

140
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:21,720
Goodbye!

141
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,600
Goodbye!

142
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,640
Final call for flight CA 1866.

143
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,920
Would Miss Shi Yi

144
